{"tid":805011,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯贏波摩佬牙擦：夠疆炒我？賠錢賠到你窮呀！","createTime":"2018-09-03T12:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T04:52:01.000Z","uid":54373,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0e13565efa0506f8a1553e98380376ece4a55b0b","tid":805011,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180903/large/1535970433_116c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180903%2Flarge%2F1535970433_116c.jpg&h=b6c760b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n摩連奴表示從未擔心會被曼聯辭退<br />\n<br />\n曼聯領隊摩連奴表示，從沒擔心自己會遭球會解僱，因為球會方面將需要付出一筆高昂的賠償金。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯周日以2:0擊敗般尼，終止兩連敗頹勢，賽後摩連奴一臉風騷，在記者會上更與記者談笑風生。被問及近期盛傳他將會被解僱一事，他打趣地回應：「有人說我的職位有危機，但我不這麼認為，因為他們這樣做的話，你知道他們要給我多少錢嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴對傳媒的態度一向起伏甚大，上星期曼聯0:3不敵熱刺後，他在賽後記者會上老羞成怒，表示自己贏得英超的次數比其餘19位領隊加起來還要多，之後更一邊離開現場，一邊叫在場的記者要給予尊重。"},{"pid":"afe5e2c8f8e03bc9b435a377259b8434dcd1bc8b","tid":805011,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續教"},{"pid":"81ace421eb389d9fb88c4cdcf1e1a3a698c88872","tid":805011,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:41:16.000Z","msg":"夠彊佢就賣普巴啦<br />\n冇撚用～"},{"pid":"426810f5b18d435b54c48410aedc389de8bd4c93","tid":805011,"uid":119729,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T14:27:25.000Z","msg":"上次叫人尊重<br />\n今次就串曼聯畀唔起錢<br />\n<br />\n知唔知曼聯每年賺幾多？<br />\n尊重啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3dabcda6229ed28f58afab6b5086d5b2f8aa7e","tid":805011,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T14:46:32.000Z","msg":"牙朗d息夠俾啦"},{"pid":"d662e1c4614cd22